On March 9, a conference is being held in the capital of Egypt on the creation of a new united Libyan government and the organization of presidential elections in the country.
The following senior Libyan government officials are taking part in the event:

-Chairman of the House of Representatives Akilah Saleh;
- Chairman of the Presidential Council Muhammad Al-Manfi;
-Chairman of the Supreme State Council Muhammad Takala.African Corps
